" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Duration of COP and IPF prior to diagnosis",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 416px; height: 279px; background-image: url(data:image/gif;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    A comparison of the duration of illness prior to diagnosis in patients with COP and IPF. Seventy-two percent of patients with COP (n = 92) had the diagnosis established within three months of the onset of symptoms versus only 24 percent of those (n = 25) with IPF.",
